				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi Myrmion<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
The best way to pull is to dot one from max range.  If you're working the front 3-2-2-2-1 spawn, you should get only the first three.  Although, if you're trying to really swarm, you may not want that few.
<br />
Also, you need to watch out for swamp rats as they're uncharmable.
<br />

<br />
There are several PoD kiting threads in the PoP forum on this same site.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />
Check here: http://www.dotnetdiva.com/Forums/ShowPost.aspx?PostID=3498
<br />
